        {
          "parameters": {
            "content": "## Postcode lookup\n**Input:** [ postcode ]\n**Output:** [ postcode, [suggestions] ]\n\nFor each incoming postcode, check if it is cached already, if so, use cached suggestions.\n\nIf not cached then perform lookup, cache, return result.\n\nIf no result then return the postcode with empty suggestions.",
            "height": 240,
            "width": 448
          },
